Package de.espirit.firstspirit.server.mediamanagement.exif

Interface ExifTags

  • public interface ExifTags
    Definition of common and specialized vendor specific Exif tags.

    Note: The Exif-Framework is not limited to this collection of exif tags. To create own tag's provide an own implementation of ExifTag. For further descriptions, tags see http://www.exif.org/Exif2-2.PDF or the manufacturer definitions.

    Since:
    5.0.100
    See Also:
    ExifData, ExifValue, ExifValueFormatter, ExifTags
